{"tid":347340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中環人語】飲恨騰訊 李澤楷身家「差啲」多過老豆","createTime":"2017-08-04T17:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T01:23:03.000Z","uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"61adf07e12d927c9c406c185b920a0c90c0128cd","tid":347340,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:36:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20170804/536045\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20170804%2F536045&d=WXy6%2FEefggLTTy5in0AyrsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=0eb30565\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20170804%2F536045&h=095c1d9b\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20170804/536045</a><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n股市靠着幾隻股票有秩序地發圍，投資銀行家喺中環坐低都離不開講住隻「股王」&mdash;&mdash;騰訊（700），有口痕友話：「當年Richard Li如果唔係咁早賣走騰訊，家陣身家多過佢老豆！」此話何來？<br />\n<br />\n追溯至一九九九年，騰訊創辦人馬化騰僅廿八歲，即創立QQ不到兩年之時，騰訊面臨財困，那時李澤楷乘科網股氣勢，正部署收購香港電訊，並且睇中QQ之潛力，灑胡椒粉咁斥資$860萬入股騰訊兩成股權，只是李澤楷蛇吞象買入香港電訊後自己亦債台高築，急於出售非核心的業務還債，遂於二○○一年，把兩成騰訊股份以$9,800萬賣咗俾南非傳媒王國Naspers旗下的MIH，雖然電盈賺咗近億，但又有誰料到，如李澤楷揸到依家，此金蛋以今天騰訊每股$316計，市值六千億元，身家仲唔係多過佢老豆？<br />\n<br />\n按福布斯2017年排名，李嘉誠身家為$2,489億，李澤楷為$340億。李澤楷只有兩個字&mdash;&mdash;「飲恨！」因為騰訊六千億元加現有身家340億元，即係6340億元，福布斯排名即刻可以由全球第385彈上第二，僅次於身家6708億元的首富蓋茨，及勁過身家5897億元的巴菲特，遠遠拋離老豆。但因為一早賣走騰訊，現實係老豆身家遠遠拋離佢！<br />\n<br />\n相反，南非佬控制的Naspers繼續加碼，現時成為騰訊大股東，佔33.25%，不過互聯網業務涉及國家安全，Naspers的大股東是南非政府的主權基金Public Investment Corporation of South Africa），○七年，工商銀行以五十五億美元入股非洲最大嘅銀行&mdash;&mdash;Standard Bank Group兩成股權，透過「鍊」住間非洲最大嘅銀行，多少對Naspers發揮到影響力，阿爺就有安全感啦。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：宗菁華"},{"pid":"717ba099d67ebd3750d4668fb0016f46177e9003","tid":347340,"uid":6558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T18:02:46.000Z","msg":"屌 佢老豆嘅遲早咪又係佢嘅"},{"pid":"6871a14343710040ad302c010e1527d076e37ba8","tid":347340,"uid":41245,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T18:08:29.000Z","msg":"唔明依啲嘢有咩人有興趣睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b76427b56c1176c6f48744104712ecd55087faa5","tid":347340,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T18:15:00.000Z","msg":"會唔會佢地知道香港有幾多分之幾係佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"326f8298ed6379172c785de4dad3dbd875613017","tid":347340,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T18:18:19.000Z","msg":"關我撚事"},{"pid":"41f19713e37cef7023c994ce8a5dff061cd54fb5","tid":347340,"uid":29804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T00:30:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 佢老豆嘅遲早咪又係佢嘅</blockquote><br />\n佢老豆嘅係李澤鉅 唔係佢"},{"pid":"929cea8b9ac8a5dae72152d9d6d2c409b7fdca90","tid":347340,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T00:54:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b93a29b4548897111e5a4b9cd953582728027797","tid":347340,"uid":37596,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T00:59:07.000Z","msg":"如果無賣，支那隨時叫李送股份俾國家，連9千萬都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3379667b74614ac272d6621dd9f2cb0e8a9ab1","tid":347340,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T01:04:49.000Z","msg":"騰訊 第一個買家係一個香港發展商<br />\n當年馬化騰 300萬求佢買"},{"pid":"4916cfde1490558cd12fced044bd1242e5456c97","tid":347340,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T01:09:05.000Z","msg":"啲錢都係多到洗唔晒啦， 多個零同少個零啫"},{"pid":"4a898d307c134f195c70cd5af0724dc3a400e50a","tid":347340,"uid":1367,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T01:09:41.000Z","msg":"如果<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你估二少會唔會用lee d野打飛機.<br />\nOn9<br />\n<br />\n屈到政府起個cyberport勁過買700啦"},{"pid":"bcafb832f7395c2f5995088d0a596a6addff85c2","tid":347340,"uid":38316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T01:37:26.000Z","msg":"李澤楷不嬲無嘜料到<br />\n成日要老豆接濟"},{"pid":"50055bdf2bc30dde261b4b95eaa7f2fc9679f2aa","tid":347340,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T02:22:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>李澤楷不嬲無嘜料到<br />\n成日要老豆接濟</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae12ca253635cdda1397008fd18aedc7a2acf011","tid":347340,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T02:26:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>李澤楷不嬲無嘜料到<br />\n成日要老豆接濟</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n查下佢軍師 袁天帆 咩料先"},{"pid":"6fe7fe328c9dac33ad0bc1a50c597e3cf018edd2","tid":347340,"uid":68802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T02:31:16.000Z","msg":"個個有入過700都會後悔啦<br />\n得好少人估到會上到咁高<br />\n係咁架啦"},{"pid":"b3a1177c3979a54931f7327834e44423ec3f8b20","tid":347340,"uid":40979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T02:35:15.000Z","msg":"白痴低質文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2476ac70c32f58b2d4d43d01f220c54826f620c0","tid":347340,"uid":50674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T02:36:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>李澤楷不嬲無嘜料到<br />\n成日要老豆接濟</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n查下佢軍師 袁天帆 咩料先</blockquote><br />\n佢可以分唔到邊個李澤鉅邊個李澤楷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67283ec623a1e1c50c641ebc5ebe9ac77c3c306d","tid":347340,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T02:36:42.000Z","msg":"地產股普遍低估值"},{"pid":"1de19446d3df3c086ae09df5d4043fe631a3cd8f","tid":347340,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T03:43:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>李澤楷不嬲無嘜料到<br />\n成日要老豆接濟</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n李澤楷衰咗幾鑊次次都係老豆拍膊頭搵人注資搵人幫拖<br />\n呢個已經係公開秘密"},{"pid":"d36ab534c51380b3f6b2577b4e60677a181df981","tid":347340,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T04:04:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1d62f39339bb21444dcc45f2cb5160be7cb2891","tid":347340,"uid":35867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T04:12:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個個有入過700都會後悔啦<br />\n得好少人估到會上到咁高<br />\n係咁架啦</blockquote><br />\n分別係普通人得自己同朋友自己研究<br />\n佢有成班金融team分析</blockquote><br />\n金融team 識分析，自己都訓咗身啦。<br />\n不過我唔排除有人訓身買咗，發咗。"},{"pid":"a3b4d5c18425f8096b4aed8f532cfce46b74f2c3","tid":347340,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T04:26:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>個個有入過700都會後悔啦<br />\n得好少人估到會上到咁高<br />\n係咁架啦</blockquote><br />\n分別係普通人得自己同朋友自己研究<br />\n佢有成班金融team分析</blockquote><br />\n金融team 識分析，自己都訓咗身啦。<br />\n不過我唔排除有人訓身買咗，發咗。</blockquote><br />\n記者在騰訊的股東登記名冊，找到報住太古城綠楊閣的陳太。按了門鐘，戴着老花眼鏡的她來應門，她斜眼對記者耍手，打發着說：「無咩好講啦，申請完就放喺度，不用理它。（為什麼不賣？之前見到升得很高。）很高便很高，不用理會它的！（不急用錢，便由它？）對，沒有錯。」說起騰訊，陳太便心情輕鬆：「（等到留給子女？）對呀，你真是！你訪問馬生吧（指馬化騰）！不用訪問陳生（她老公）。」之後她匆匆關門。陳太在騰訊上市時，成功申請了五千股；以當時招股價三元七角計，價值一萬八千五百元。其後騰訊輾轉向上，曾升上五百多元，到一四年股份一拆五，陳太變相揸二萬五千股，再繼續升。計一計數，這批原先萬多元的股份，升了三百倍，價值已變成五百四十萬！"},{"pid":"586010802516c8028e01959f55bbfb62815397fb","tid":347340,"uid":2394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T04:31:17.000Z","msg":"屌 你啲錢咪又係你老豆嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92847a8e2ce65b88e441f5a7e845a353ab8d85b3","tid":347340,"uid":74368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T04:34:29.000Z","msg":"如果佢仲係大股東既話, 700就可能冇今日<br />\n大陸會唔會咁俾錢你賺俾你獨大<br />\n仲有佢賣左可以投資其他野度賺錢"},{"pid":"10aee943dc75dd071d9bb9505629da1ee199b3f8","tid":347340,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T04:41:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 佢老豆嘅遲早咪又係佢嘅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n長和系分左比大仔窩"}]}